    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban rotating shift patterns and require 4 weeks' notice of zero hours rota",
        "additional_details": "This is to protect and improve lowest paid workers health and wellbeing and encourage them to stay in or start employment. Many find rotating shifts a huge barrier and many of production / warehouse jobs are on such shifts.",
        "background": "Rotating days/nights or early/late shifts are detrimental for worker\u2019s health and wellbeing. We believe the majority of shift workers would prefer a permanent shift but many are stuck in rotating arrangements. Also make it compulsory to publish rota for zero hours staff at least 4 weeks in advance",
